   21: %%%-------------------------------------------------------------------
   22: %%% File: master_SUITE
   23: %%%
   24: %%% Description:
   25: %%% Test suite for common_test which tests the ct_master functionality
   26: %%%-------------------------------------------------------------------
   27: -module(master_SUITE).
   28: 
   29: -compile(export_all).
   30: 
   31: -include_lib("common_test/include/ct.hrl").
   32: -include("test.hrl").
   33: 
   34: suite() ->
   35:     [].
   36: 
   37: init_per_suite(Config) ->
   38:     Config.
   39: 
   40: end_per_suite(_) ->
   41:     ok.
   42: 
   43: all() -> [first_testcase, second_testcase, third_testcase,
   44: 	  env_vars].
   45: 
   46: init_per_testcase(_, Config) ->
   47:     Config.
   48: 
   49: end_per_testcase(_, _) ->
   50:     ok.
   51: 
   52: first_testcase(_)->
   53:     b = ct:get_config(a).
   54: 
   55: second_testcase(_)->
   56:     d = ct:get_config(c).
   57: 
   58: third_testcase(_)->
   59:     A = 4,
   60:     A = 2*2.
   61: 
   62: env_vars(_) ->
   63:     io:format("~p\n", [os:getenv()]),
   64:     "yes" = os:getenv("THIS_MUST_BE_SET"),
   65:     "value" = os:getenv("SO_MUST_THIS"),
   66:     ok.
